  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Set the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ 400°F/ Gas 6</p><p>Cut the <strong>Romano</strong> <strong>pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>and <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> to a baking tray, drizzle with <strong>olive oil </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20 minutes or until softened</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1579.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1579.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1579.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1579.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1579.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and chop the <strong>potatoes</strong> into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Strip the <strong>thyme leaves</strong> and chop them roughly, discarding the stems</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1579.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1579.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1579.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1579.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1579.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> and <strong>thyme</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 25-30 minutes or until golden and crispy</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1579.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1579.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
