    {
      "instruction": "<p>Re-boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> monkfish fillets</strong> and cook for 3-4 minutes. Add a knob of <strong>butter</strong>, flip the <strong>fish</strong> and cook for 3-4 minutes further or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque</p>",
      "order": 6,
